搞兩岸政治對抗，一邊要求大陸惠台措施只增不減，這個世界上哪有這樣的邏輯？出了問題以後，<span class=\"red\">台灣一些人還叫嚷&ldquo;自由鳳梨（菠蘿）&rdquo;，對比澳大利亞的&ldquo;自由紅酒&rdquo;</span>，這不是給台灣果農挖坑嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T18:32:18.000Z","msg":"制裁ASUS, TSM,MTK<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a59e16493eb8707abd71c0b57222981a9d7b68","tid":2426011,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T03:57:20.000Z","msg":"台灣全面禁運晶片俾中港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ded607fbe99c3466b27393fcb9070238e0ef630","tid":2426011,"uid":166080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T03:58:16.000Z","msg":"全面禁止台灣晶片"},{"pid":"61f44f1ad411c2eeca61799483ac04c8e4f0bc0b","tid":2426011,"uid":36254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T04:00:05.000Z","msg":"咪撚買晶片啦"},{"pid":"c2a82bb752097ee36a51f350d6a9ab598a745ca7","tid":2426011,"uid":195858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T04:01:27.000Z","msg":"呢條總編真係打呢份喉舌工好稱職"},{"pid":"b35d59a9eed383c5b4ff99649bce314b3d200831","tid":2426011,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7853833b4a5d7af7422a382b2f6e2b86d4985589","tid":2426011,"uid":179775,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T17:37:56.000Z","msg":"屌 之前夠話唔放人去旅行餓死台灣人<br />\n<br />\n最後呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T04:12:23.000Z","msg":"台灣人可以唔帶口罩咩都做得"},{"pid":"eec52b269a058bc7c189dc299fa269b0f5d8f102","tid":2426011,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T04:20:55.000Z","msg":"石頭 腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56bb30c2cb8a9f9a597b2e5d140cfe8183c3a624","tid":2426011,"uid":274996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T04:21:27.000Z","msg":"成日話外國冇咗中國唔得，但其實中國係高度依賴外國，次次制裁都係搞到自己，只不過中國韭菜夠多夠賤，用生命值硬接。"},{"pid":"06a771823f6a5486f1ac77d033e690b7dc5ddbf3","tid":2426011,"uid":53026,"like":0,"disli