\"red\">台灣一些人還叫嚷&ldquo;自由鳳梨（菠蘿）&rdquo;，對比澳大利亞的&ldquo;自由紅酒&rdquo;</span>，這不是給台灣果農挖坑嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:29:57.000Z","msg":"台灣以後唔賣晶片俾大陸, 睇吓邊個滿地找牙"},{"pid":"32e92a49db0762f39a04eba593c501a9d57c3e56","tid":2426011,"uid":357710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbb5012d593ad15a3ed6b300a09cf69e49075fd1","tid":2426011,"uid":15830,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T17:36:18.000Z","msg":"制裁台積電啲貨未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:49:54.000Z","msg":"是台積電自己話生意夠做，堅持唔賣大陸播。"},{"pid":"4cf7eca3563825aa41bf61a77bcfdbf49d89944c","tid":2426011,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2c490cb49edf44047ccdff6845de4a85619025c","tid":2426011,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b303ec4c1a6771438a001ad61509ff521bedb2d5","tid":2426011,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:00:29.000Z","msg":"又話台灣是中国的一部份<br />\n又話中国人自己人不打自己人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死漢奸胡錫進"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T06:01:43.000Z","msg":"中国人自己人不打自己人<br />\n<br />\n笑話黎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:42:08.000Z","msg":"中國人專殺中國人"},{"pid":"3bc3051f26d564afb565b7482eb5bd8149edf6c9","tid":2426011,"uid":131600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:43:22.000Z","msg":"敢唔敢自由晶片？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09c83df814af5380af2d86c0b29af6e7c76776e","tid":2426011,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3ccfcb24e42a65c44268bbc8732c965f2a1f74a","tid":2426011,"uid":35393,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T04:25:36.000Z","msg":"操你妈的，胡狗，你这个台独分裂分子。台湾是中国的，那么中国人会制裁中国人吗？你这样说就是破坏中国人民感情，企图颠覆国家政权。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"reply